http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0295971789/natilangofthe-20
">To Please The Caribou</A>:</B><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Art book display of painted caribou-skin coats of the Innu, Cree, and Atikameks of Quebec and Labrador. 
